{"tid":2479320,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人知Leo man文生 死左去邊","createTime":"2021-04-07T17:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-08T03:01:07.000Z","uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"deaf58732fca30e9b2484f4e7ed84ad078bf03b7","tid":2479320,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:45:35.000Z","msg":"在《100毛》、Beauty Exchange、《東方日報》、《蘋果日報》、名校Secrets等facebook專頁中，均也看到Leo Man這個黑人的留言。<br />\n<br />\n該黑人就好像不用休息、睡覺一樣，由早到晚都會不斷留言。由於其留言用字精要及搞笑，加上其回覆網友的速度非常快，因此他亦很快便儲下一班固定的粉絲，粉絲們更直言上facebook是為了遇到那個黑人；在10個facebook專頁帖子中，當中有9個也會看到有網友積極留言：「又係你呀文生。」<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月初，Leo Man在其Facebook專頁宣布將發行著作《又係你呀文生》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早幾年成日出現 開埋fb page又出書<br />\n上埋電視/新聞比人訪問<br />\n依家就消失左連page都冇埋"},{"pid":"fd8b4f09b370c9849ed6774f5caae6b7338641c1","tid":2479320,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:48:34.000Z","msg":"黑人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b73bb18c786d79d8896691751700520a7248b48","tid":2479320,"uid":367769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:48:43.000Z","msg":"唔講都唔記得咗呢個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣見到心諗咁都出到書做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2109a29eb183b5985b11c757338608ed431506fd","tid":2479320,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.cp1897.com.hk/bookinfo/image/450/9789888445479z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cp1897.com.hk%2Fbookinfo%2Fimage%2F450%2F9789888445479z.jpg&h=3a83bb9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cad10c9618c1ab3de5697de33ff7b80209d49e7b","tid":2479320,"uid":116696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T02:48:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62cf503d1d11ee9236fc8a103cfc7b57e831c75b"